summary: Level 38 Nord named Haruhi. Currently located at Blizzard\'s Rest. She is a Stormcloak and currently married to Vilkas.
descriptionHtml:
I have finished the main quest, along with the following main quests;
Stormcloaks
Dark Brotherhood
College of Winterhold
Bard\'s College
The Companions
(I\'m also in the Thieve\'s Guild but I haven\'t finished the last special job or the Unusual Gems)

I\'m a thane every where except in the Pale. I also have bought all the houses. Argis, Calder and Iona are part of the Blades. I don\'t know where Jordis went.

The following are available for followers (excluding people that can be bought/companions/DB initiates):
Mjoll the Lioness
Onmund
J\'zargo
Brelyna Maryon
Sven

Mod I use:
Killable Children - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6450
Apachii Hair - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168
Populated Cities - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9201

Blades Faction Fix - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=8426
